            <![CDATA[
            <h3>Version 2.0.71 - Faster Initial Progress Send</h3>

            <h4>Bug Fixes</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Fix slow position bar for Basic SCORM: replaced fixed 1000ms timeout with fast 200ms retry mechanism</li>
                <li>Initial progress now sends as soon as LMSInitialize completes (~200ms) instead of waiting the full 1000ms</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>Changes</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Retry every 200ms for up to 5 attempts: send initial progress as soon as lesson_location is available</li>
                <li>Early total slides detection runs on each retry attempt</li>
                <li>Falls back to previous behavior after 1000ms if data still unavailable</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>Previous Versions</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>v2.0.70: Early total slides detection before initial progress send</li>
                <li>v2.0.69: Preserve SCORM score-based progress in activity progress API</li>
                <li>v2.0.68: Fix progress 0% on resume, score &gt;100%, false completion</li>
            </ul>
            ]]>
